0.3.0:
	* Portability fixes

0.2.1:
	* Add/update license/copyrights
	* Do not distribute .d files

0.2.0: Rewrite carbon compiler in carbon itself.

0.1.5:
	* Allow identifiers in switch-case statements.
	* [bugfix] Make sure the visitor visites the whole tree.
	* Change operator precedence for IS_OF to parse: !obj is_of class
	* Add <Class>.class expression
	* [bugfix] Handle nested function in class methods properly
	* Allow the use of self in interface methods and raise error when used incorrectly.
	* Use macro to check for implementation of interface.
	* Generate 'interface instances' as Object
	* [bugfix] Lookup identifiers upon declaration

0.1.4:
	* [bugfix] Use conditional cast when casting objects or interfaces
	* Add option -d/--depend to generate dependency information to be used by Makefiles
	* Change -P option to -I, to align better with existing compilers
	* Add mixin: Allow interface methods to have an implementation
	* Add nested functions
	* Add syntax to avoid name clashes for implementing multiple interfaces

0.1.3:
	* Switch-case statement added
	* Syntax change for implementing interfaces: [ ',' INTERFACE ]*
	* [bugfix] Generate #inlude statement for all externally defined tokens
	* [bugfix] Do not generate a function when the body is undefined

0.1.2: Bugfix release
	* [bugfix] Raise error when function expression is not a function type
	* [bugfix] Set the parent scope of class members before type checking
	* [bugfix] Add typedef for undeclared types first used in function prototype

0.1.1:
	* Add ConditionalBinaryExpression
	* Allow expression for the class in IS_OF expression

0.1.0: Initial release
